description: Youyeetoo recently listed a motherboard based on the MediaTek Genio 510/700 platform, built around the MT8390 and MT8370 processors. The X8390ABV4 MediaTek Development Board includes Gigabit Ethernet, dual-band Wi-Fi, and multiple multimedia interfaces, making it applicable for AI and IoT applications. The MT8390 features an octa-core processor with two ARM Cortex-A78 cores clocked at 2.2GHz […]
title: X8390ABV4 Development Board with MediaTek Genio 510/700 and PCIe Expansion
